---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ByteCapsule from '../assets/bytecapsuleit.jpeg';
import WIYP from '../assets/wellington.png';
import Fiverr from '../assets/fiverr-logo.png';
import AZGroup from '../assets/azgroup-logo.svg';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section
  class="my-10 flex w-full flex-col items-center border-l border-gray-300 p-3 dark:border-slate-700 md:flex-row md:items-start"
  data-animate
>
  <h1 class="mr-10 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-400">Experience</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-10">
    <!-- Experience 3 -->
    <div
      class="rounded-sm border-l-2 border-sky-400 bg-slate-50 p-4 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 dark:bg-slate-800/50"
    >
      <div class="flex w-full justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="mx-5">
            <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
              <Image
                src={AZGroup}
                alt="AZ Group logo"
                class="mr-2 h-6 w-6"
                width={24}
                height={24}
              />
              <h1 class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold dark:text-slate-200">
                AZ Group
                <span>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.az-group.io/butly-ai"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  >
                    <Icon name="gridicons:external" class="ml-2 text-sky-400" width="18" />
                  </a>
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">Lead Software Developer</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">Nov, 2023 - Present</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="ml-5 mt-4 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li>Architected and led full-stack development of Butly AI, an enterprise-grade AI-powered customer support platform.</li>
        <li>Designed a multi-LLM orchestration layer that intelligently routes queries across multiple Large Language Models for contextually accurate, low-latency responses.</li>
        <li>Established engineering standards, code review processes, and CI/CD pipelines that reduced deployment friction across the team.</li>
        <li>Collaborated directly with stakeholders to translate product vision into scalable technical architecture.</li>
        <li>Owned both infrastructure and core application development end-to-end.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience: Fiverr -->
    <div
      class="rounded-sm border-l-2 border-sky-400 bg-slate-50 p-4 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 dark:bg-slate-800/50"
    >
      <div class="flex w-full justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="mx-5">
            <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
              <Image
                src={Fiverr}
                alt="Fiverr logo"
                class="mr-2 h-6 w-6"
                width={24}
                height={24}
                format="avif"
              />
              <h1 class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold dark:text-slate-200">
                Fiverr
                <span>
                  <a href="https://fiverr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <Icon name="gridicons:external" class="ml-2 text-sky-400" width="18" />
                  </a>
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">Level 2 Seller</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">Sept, 2022 - Present</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="ml-5 mt-4 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li>Delivered 50+ AWS infrastructure and full-stack engagements as a top-rated Level 2 freelancer.</li>
        <li>Maintained a consistent 5-star rating across all projects.</li>
        <li>Architected serverless solutions on AWS — leveraging Lambda, API Gateway, DynamoDB, and ECS — that reduced client infrastructure costs by up to 60% compared to traditional server setups.</li>
        <li>Specialized in end-to-end MERN stack application delivery, from database schema design through production deployment.</li>
        <li>Consistently exceeded client expectations on performance, scalability, and security.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience 2 -->
    <div
      class="rounded-sm border-l-2 border-sky-400 bg-slate-50 p-4 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 dark:bg-slate-800/50"
    >
      <div class="flex w-full justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="mx-5">
            <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
              <Image
                src={WIYP}
                alt="Wellington In Your Pocket logo"
                class="mr-2 h-6 w-6"
                width={24}
                height={24}
                format="avif"
              />
              <h1 class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold dark:text-slate-200">
                Wellington In Your Pocket
                <span>
                  <a
                    href="https://wellingtoninyourpocket.co.nz/home2/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  >
                    <Icon name="gridicons:external" class="ml-2 text-sky-400" width="18" />
                  </a>
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">Cloud Engineer</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">Jan, 2023 - Sept, 2023</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="ml-5 mt-4 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li>Designed and implemented the scalable backend cloud infrastructure on AWS supporting the Wellington In Your Pocket platform.</li>
        <li>Architected high-availability solutions using EC2, RDS, and CloudFront, ensuring the platform could handle peak traffic reliably.</li>
        <li>Introduced automated CI/CD pipelines that cut deployment time by over 80%.</li>
        <li>Drove a cloud cost optimization initiative that reduced monthly AWS spend by 40%.</li>
        <li>Worked cross-functionally with product, design, and QA teams to translate business requirements into robust, production-ready cloud solutions.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience 1 -->
    <div
      class="rounded-sm border-l-2 border-sky-400 bg-slate-50 p-4 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 dark:bg-slate-800/50"
    >
      <div class="flex w-full justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="mx-5">
            <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
              <Image
                src={ByteCapsule}
                alt="Byte Capsule Ltd logo"
                class="mr-2 h-6 w-6"
                width={24}
                height={24}
                format="avif"
              />
              <h1 class="flex items-center text-lg font-semibold dark:text-slate-200">
                Byte Capsule Ltd.
                <span>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.bytecapsuleit.com/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  >
                    <Icon name="gridicons:external" class="ml-2 text-sky-400" width="18" />
                  </a>
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">Operations Lead</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">May, 2020 - Nov, 2022</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="ml-5 mt-4 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li>Led operations and technical service delivery at a fast-growing cybersecurity startup.</li>
        <li>Conducted application security assessments and penetration testing for enterprise clients, identifying and remediating critical vulnerabilities before production exposure.</li>
        <li>Designed and delivered cybersecurity training curricula educating over 1,000 students across multiple universities, establishing the company as a credible security education provider.</li>
        <li>Represented the organization as a keynote speaker at industry conferences and university webinars, strengthening brand visibility.</li>
        <li>Streamlined internal workflows and cross-team collaboration, measurably improving operational efficiency across the organization.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
